text.tspan: Cheesecake
This is a cheesecake like no other, with a soft cream mix that’s perfectly formed to create a
sinfully delicate texture, it’s the best made-from-scratch cheesecake you will ever have!
Focaccia with Marinara
A basket of made from scratch freshly baked Italian yeast bread served
with warm marinara sauce and an herb infused extra virgin olive oil
Savory Puff Pastries
Chicken Marsala with Fettuccine
Tender chicken breast paired with sautéed baby bella mushrooms, all simmered in a luxurious blend
of rich stock and Marsala wine, tossed in our freshly made fettuccine pasta. This dish offers an
elegant fusion of flavors that promises to satisfy.
Chicken Piccata with Fettuccine
Succulent chicken breast sautéed to perfection in a luscious sauce made with rich butter, white
wine and zesty capers, sliced and tossed in our freshly made fettuccine pasta. This delightful dish
creates a harmonious blend of flavors and textures that elevates the palate

Chicken Cacciatore Stuffed Shells
Shrimp Fettucine in a Creamy White Sauce
Summer Peaches and Cream Cake
Savor the delicate flavors of large, tender shrimp sautéed in a velvety white cream sauce, paired
with our freshly handmade fettuccine. This luxurious dish combines the perfect balance of succulent
shrimp and creamy sauce, enveloping each pasta strand in rich, indulgent goodness.
Indulge in our hearty Chicken Cacciatore Stuffed Shells, generously filled with tender chicken
cacciatore and a creamy blend of Ricotta, Pecorino Romano, and Mozzarella cheeses. Baked in a
rich cacciatore sauce, these shells offer a comforting experience with every bite
Delight in our baked-to-perfection savory golden-brown puff pastries. Each
bite offers a flaky, buttery crust with a deliciously rich and flavorful
interior of seasonal vegetables and fresh herbs
